Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:02.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Victory! Honesty! The shocking evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.80,0:00:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The inexhaustible drive to aim for the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.51,0:00:05.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The popular series is finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:07.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An unexpected meeting at a singles party!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.68,0:00:09.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The love of the police detectives hits the brakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:10.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:12.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body of a child and the brains of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:14.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.16,0:01:51.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so you can't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.70,0:01:52.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, some work that I can't just leave suddenly came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:01:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if it's work I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.92,0:02:04.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh right, tell that man not to drink too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:09.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he gets drunk, becomes involved with the young\Ngirls there and causes a problem, I won't be his lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:10.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.01,0:02:12.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk to you later, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:24.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with that sigh when\Nwe're just about to eat a great meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.32,0:02:25.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you asked Auntie Eri to come here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:31.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured that might be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you suddenly said "A stylish cafe just opened,\Nlet's go check it out," I knew there was something behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:41.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:45.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Liar. When you found out it was\Ngood and cheap, you were crazy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:49.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was really difficult to get a\Nreservation at this place, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:52.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not such a bad place...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:56.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Except for all the annoying\Nyoung people and their group dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.35,0:02:58.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Isn't that Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:00.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Chiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:04.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Detective Takagi's here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:07.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's all this then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:10.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two men having dinner together at a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:11.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:13.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just a singles party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:15.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wha? You idiot! I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:18.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Singles party?" Does Detective Sato know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:23.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no! I'm only here to even out the numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:25.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chiba forced me to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right? That's right, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:28.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:32.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even thought that's true, when you\Nsay it that way it sounds like you're lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So please keep this a secret from Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:45.86,Signs,,0,0,0,,THE METROPOLITAN POLICE\NDETECTIVE LOVE STORY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:45.86,Signs,,0,0,0,,(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One more time, cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:52.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo, Chiba. You're late you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:55.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The girls are really into it; they've already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.66,0:03:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.12,0:03:58.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:03.33,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,This is my friend from my middle school days\Nand the ringleader of our singles party, Emoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:04.51,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Emoto Masashi (26)\NSports Gym Trainer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:04.51,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:09.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Detective Mouri. We just bumped into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:13.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know you! You're Sleeping Kogoro, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, is the "buddy" you mentioned here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:20.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is my coworker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, nice to meet you, I'm Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:27.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, he's a bit dull-looking,\Nbut it's better than having no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:30.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this guy has a bad mouth, but he's good at heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:32.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Chiba, we're really lucky today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:40.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're there among the woman\Nwho came today. Two cute babes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so? That's great, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your sister was planning to come\Ntoday. Could she be one of those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.59,0:04:54.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of them is one of my sister's old friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:05:00.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the other is that girl's good friend or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:03.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both of them do some kind of police related work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:05.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Police related?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:05.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Police related?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:09.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Chiba, in the past you used to say\Nyou wanted to become a policeman or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:11.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what are you doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:14.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, I'm a police detective. A detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:18.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then that dull-looking guy is a policeman too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:19.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:23.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then maybe you've already met them somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:25.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two policewomen in mini-skirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:27.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mini-skirts?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:30.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure those two are really police officers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:33.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this isn't TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's OK, isn't it? I do it 'cause I\Ncan't wear showy stuff while on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:42.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? It's Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Chiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! What're ya doin' here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you guys knew each other after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:52.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.69,0:05:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other person...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:55.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:05:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't handle all those guys by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:05.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:06.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What's she doings here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}? And Chiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mood's getting dangerous, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heh, it's starting to get interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.43,0:06:19.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:25.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so you see, the culprit came rushing at me like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I got his joint like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:31.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I be the culprit next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:34.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave it to Detective Sato to monopolize all the men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well that's no big deal. The real problem is that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You figured out the trick in that last case too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:45.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell us about it, tell us about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:49.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was so easy that I've forgotten how it was done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, you're so cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:57.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should be going soon I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:06:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey hey, what are you saying, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly, you're supposed to be relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.93,0:07:06.02,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Emoto Aya(28)\NIllustrator
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:06.02,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,But I'm worried about Kouta\Nwatching the house all by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, is he your little brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:11.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he's my cousin who's just turning five.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His parents are both overseas on business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we're taking care of him at our house for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:22.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You fixed his dinner before we came.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:24.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You need to get out of that apartment once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I still have work left to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's forget about work for today at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:32.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not taking a breather every so\Noften can be bad for your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:33.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:38.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:41.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:42.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:45.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I really ought to be going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.18,0:07:47.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So many strange things happened before this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:48.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange things?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:50.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Things to do with Kouta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:52.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like the Kamen Yaiba battle card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.27,0:07:54.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Battle card?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:59.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The other day Kouta\Nbrought his friends over to show it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:02.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a super rare card that I hadn't seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said a nice man gave it to him or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:07.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a man with long bangs and a beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:10.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'd dropped his wallet in front of Kouta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:13.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he picked it up for him,\Nhe was given that card in thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:20.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, that man took Kouta to his home, brought\Nout some cake for him and asked him a lot of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was he asked?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:28.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kouta said the man was a fortune\Nteller and he asked about our apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.18,0:08:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Things like where his bed was, where things were in the\Nentryway, and when my brother's and my birthdays were.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:37.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He even asked where we keep our mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:39.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:41.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kouta told him I keep mine in a box inside the closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.11,0:08:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that my brother leaves his out on top of his desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:50.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy said those were really\Ngood spots and not to move them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:56.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anything important in your mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:08:58.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, nothing particularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:00.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing in mine either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:04.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, that man is apparently one of my buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:06.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:11.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's probably just planning to surprise\Nme by doing something for my birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:14.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you know it was your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.56,0:09:19.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kouta said there was a phone\Ncall while he was eating the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:22.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man happened to be in the\Nbathroom, so the machine picked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:27.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said the voice he heard was my voice, so it can't be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:30.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, do you have any idea who that person is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.62,0:09:35.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno. I called all over trying to\Ngather members for this singles party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, it has to be one of them, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.88,0:09:43.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that after that guy heard the\Nmessage he sent Kouta home in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was probably afraid that I would\Nfind out about it and ruin the surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say in the message?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:51.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just that my sister and I are having this\Nsingles party here the Saturday after next.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:10:01.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means that person knows\Nthe little boy is home alone tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:04.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call him right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've tried a few times but he's not answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:09.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I have to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:11.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, we have to go and check.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:14.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:15.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:16.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:19.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:26.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kouta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:28.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kouta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:33.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just being paranoid; the door was properly locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:38.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man was just asking about\Nfurniture placement and birthdays, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:40.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's probably just some feng shui guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:47.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even now there are a lot of people who use their\Nbirthday as their safe's combination so they won't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:52.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And knowing the arrangement of the furniture\Nbeforehand would make finding the safe easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:56.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or possibly the letters and postcards might\Nprovide a clue to help them infer the combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:11:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And perhaps if he couldn't achieve his objective...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit's next action would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:04.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Detectives!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:08.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:14.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:16.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have the boy; don't call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But aren't you guys police detectives?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:30.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:33.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, in some ways this makes it easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:35.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, I'll contact the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:36.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:39.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit broke into this\Napartment and kidnapped Kouta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might still be nearby watching the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If police come trooping through this house, he'd find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be no good if he picked up the\Nelectromagnetic waves from our cellphones either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:52.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can contact them after we confirm whether any\Nlistening devices have been planted somewhere or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:54.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you at least know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:11:58.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I overstated that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:11:59.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:06.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, wasn't the culprit someone who met\NKouta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} once, and might be one of this guy's friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:08.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:14.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then if you tell Uncle Kogoro about that\Ntime in detail, maybe he'll know who the culprit is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:22.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I remember right, it was two\Nweeks ago on a Saturday, right Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.29,0:12:28.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that day Kouta went out to play and\Ndidn't come back until after 8 o'clock at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:29.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eight o'clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's pretty late, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:36.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was getting worried and\Nthinking about calling the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.93,0:12:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he came home looking all innocent and said he was sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He asked me to keep it a secret from his\Nmother and father, so I didn't scold him much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:50.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd no idea he had met such a dangerous person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he had him pick up his wallet\Non purpose and brought him to his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:59.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And by chance at the same time it arrived:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:04.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My message that said my sister\Nwas joining the singles party tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:10.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. Then the kidnapper must\Ndefinitely be one of Masashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:15.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time he got Kouta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} to tell him about\Nthe arrangement of the furniture in this apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.01,0:13:18.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He planned to break in tonight when they were both away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Emoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, is there a safe in this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.14,0:13:24.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't have a silly thing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We carry our credit cards and bankbooks and such with us,\Nso there's really nothing we worry about being taken, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:37.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In short, the culprit got into the house but\Ncouldn't find anything of monetary value...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:40.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he kidnapped Kouta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:46.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, do you remember who you called\Nabout the singles party that didn't come tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:48.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. There were three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.17,0:13:52.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first one's name is Rokuda, a pal from when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:55.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The second was my junior in high school, Hikiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.84,0:13:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The third is a regular customer of\Nthe gym where I work, Satsuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:04.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All three are good guys and I can't\Nimagine them kidnapping anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:07.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the times when you called those three?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.35,0:14:09.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I called Rokuda sometime after noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:11.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I called Hikiya in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I called Satsuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} later\Nthat night, I think around 7 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All three of them were during the time\NKouta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was out, from noon until 8 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:28.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, he got cheated didn't he? After\Nthe culprit went to such elaborate preparations...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:32.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He should have made sure there was\Nsomething of monetary value to steal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.63,0:14:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Clearly, if he had wanted to kidnap\NKouta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, he could've done it those two weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then that man must have been interested in the mail, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were there any important\Nletters or official documents in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:48.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not really. Nothing that I know of anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:49.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about postcards?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it! The lottery numbers on\Nthe new year's greetings postcards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think first prize this year was a trip to Hawaii. He\Ncould sell that at a bargain ticket shop for a lot of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he made a note of the names and the\Nnumbers of the people he sent new year's cards to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look. These are the three new\Nyear's greetings cards we received.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're all losers though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Losers? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:18.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I checked all the new year's cards that were sent to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:22.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike me, my sister is really into sweepstakes and lotteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:27.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? You're the one who\Ncollects cards at your age, like you were still a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:29.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Collects cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:32.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like Kouta, but I've been doing it since I was a kid
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:37.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how old I got, I just\Ncouldn't stop collecting Kamen Yaiba cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:41.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, that's how he knew the\Ncard Kouta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} received was so rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:48.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if you think my friends are so suspicious,\Nwhy don't we take a ride over and check on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:53.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All three of them said they had things to do at\Nhome today so they couldn't come to the singles party.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:57.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good idea. Since they're all suspects, let's go and check.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:15:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if they find out you're police detectives...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:03.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll stick to the pretense that were\Nstopping by on the way home from the singles party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:04.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll keep that we came here a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:08.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, if they start behaving\Nstrangely, it's an instant confirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if they happen to be absent, they must be the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:14.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They might know Detective Mouri's face...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So please remain here with Aya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and\NRan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} and wait for the culprit to contact you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:19.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:24.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we'll take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.66,0:16:29.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This kid notices a lot of things and he\Nmight cause the culprit to lower his guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:41.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, here it is. Number 203.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:44.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this the first time you've been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:46.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, at least to his apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:50.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:52.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me, Emoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:56.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way home from the\Nsingles party. Can I come in for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:17:00.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it that brings you here so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I was talking about you at the\Nsingles party with these two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:07.74,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Rokuda Takuji (26)\NMusician
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:07.75,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Talking about me? What about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, you see, the two of us are in a band too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But his lyrics and my melodies\Nhaven't been meshing well recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:19.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, could you let me hear your songs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:22.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:24.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Is this your child?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, he's my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's pretty good, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:41.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:47.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what's this? You still have so many lottery tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:49.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You do too. Those are from the\Nyear-end lottery that I split and sent to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:52.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you checked yours properly like you should?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's OK, they'd all be losers anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:18:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How should I say it, Rokuda? If you have the money to\Nbuy all these, you should move to a better neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's something good\Nin that bulging mailbox of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:08.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.47,0:18:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! Amazing, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just like Chiba's apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:23.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! Since I admire models so\Nmuch, this is super inspirational!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:28.74,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hikika Kadonari (25)\NModeler
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:28.75,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Being admired by a beautifully\Ndesigned character like you is a real thrill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:29.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Character, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.99,0:18:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should have gone to the singles party too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I keep inviting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:42.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, what was inside the limited edition event\Npack of Yaiba cards you asked me to buy and send you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:44.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, all seven were worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.01,0:18:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same with mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That illusory Potato Queen platinum card wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the limited edition event pack?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.89,0:18:57.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a one day thing where you could only buy two packs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:04.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a rumor that in among the 7 cards in each pack\Nthere might be a super rare card that's not made anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The price for those can go over\Nalmost 800,000 yen on internet auctions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.82,0:19:09.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,800,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:12.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, cards and figures are fine and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.95,0:19:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Hikiya, you really should look\Nat some real live girls occasionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.67,0:19:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.71,0:19:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I admire old-time money so\Nmuch, this is super inspirational!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:31.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's overdoing it a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:37.78,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Satsuka Yoshikane (31)\NPaper Money Collector
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:36.53,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Oh? Then do you have some too? Like these?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:39.23,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Ah, no. Nothing special...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:44.94,Signs,,0,0,0,,Translator's note: In Japanese, many syllables can matched to numbers based on similar sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:44.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just stuff like a 10,000 yen Taishi bill with a\Nnumber that ends with my name "Miwako" (385).
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.94,0:19:51.71,Signs,,0,0,0,,Translator note: Taishi (prince) in the previous sub refers to Prince Shotoku (573-621) imperial regent and one of the early supporters of Buddhism in Japan. His portrait graced the 10,000 yen bill from 1958-1986.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should keep that safe without spending\Nit, even though it doesn't have any special value.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:53.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I should.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The valuable ones are, look, these.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, these are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:01.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The serial numbers are all the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:08.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, if you keep taking out loans to add more\Nrare bills to your collection, your wife will run out on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:11.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry about that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:15.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you get the 30,000 yen\Nrepayment I sent you through registered mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:17.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More importantly, you should start\Neating properly and come to our gym again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're really losing weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:26.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:32.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So? There wasn't anyone suspicious among those three.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:36.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, there weren't any long-haired men with beards...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was probably a disguise so that\NKouta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} wouldn't see his real face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:43.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you still suspecting them? Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:47.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kouta wasn't anywhere in any of the three guy's apartments.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:51.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the voice on the answering machine\Nmight just have been someone who sounded like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:55.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's from my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.89,0:20:58.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Could the culprit have contacted her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:20:59.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:01.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello? Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, nothing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.98,0:21:06.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's something Kouta said that's been on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.86,0:21:10.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it some characteristic of the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.61,0:21:14.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's just that when he was\Neating cake at that person's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.82,0:21:16.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems there was a baseball game on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:18.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a really boring game.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A boring game?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:29.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it took place during this season, it would be either\Nhigh school baseball or a pre-season professional game.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:32.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For now, let's have investigators\Nstakeout those three people's homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:35.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can check what baseball games were played on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.22,0:21:37.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We might be able to narrow down the suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.76,0:21:38.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.18,0:21:40.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stakeout?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:42.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you really going that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is just someone's idea of a practical joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe Kouta will show back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of brain-dead things are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.90,0:21:51.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child's been abducted!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:52.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.90,0:21:54.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A practical joke like that would be inexcusable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:21:58.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah... I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, we've\Nidentified the kidnapper!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.76,0:23:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he refuses to come along voluntarily,\Narrest him without a warrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.51,0:23:41.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:47.10,Signs,,0,0,0,,THE METROPOLITAN POLICE\NDETECTIVE LOVE STORY\N(PART TWO)
